  "slug": "exp-counter",
  "title": "EXP Counter",
  "description": "See your total XP and see exactly how much you need to level up, fully configurable",
  "body": "<h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xRZu1Om.png\" alt=\"Title\"/></h1>\n<center><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> \n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/2CUh6gMuCt\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1027252425960198165?color=5b6ee1&amp;label=Discord&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://patreon.com/MarsThePlanet\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint.svg?url=https%3A%2F%2Fshieldsio-patreon.vercel.app%2Fapi%3Fusername%3DMarsThePlanet%26type%3Dpatrons&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/exp-counter-fabric-forge-neoforge\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/1003151?color=F16436&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=Curseforge&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"CurseForge\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/exp-counter\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/exp-counter?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=modrinth&amp;color=00AF5C\" alt=\"Modrinth\" /></a>\n</strong></h5></center>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This fully configurable client-side mod displays the experience points you've gathered toward your next level, and your total accumulated XP.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kp9KDkT.png\"/></p></center>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Configuration</strong></summary>\n<p>You can configure this mod directly in-game or edit the JSON file <code>config/expcounter.json</code> in your profile folder. If you're using Fabric and want to adjust the config values in-game, you'll need to install <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/modmenu\">Mod Menu</a>.</p>\n<center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>show_next_level</b> - Whether the counter of xp collected towards the next level should be displayed</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>show_total</b> - Whether the total accumulated XP should be displayed</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>color_next_level</b> - Color of the counter of xp collected towards the next level should be displayed in decimal</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>color_total</b> - color of the total XP counter in decimal</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>position_off_centre_next_level</b> - X-axis offset off center of the xp to next level counter</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>position_y_next_level</b> - Y-axis position of the xp to next level counter</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>position_off_centre_total</b> - X-axis offset off center of the total xp counter counter</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>position_y_total</b> - Y-axis position of total xp counter</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/L8L2T3M.png\" height=\"400\"/></p>\n</center>\n</details>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JNZ2GMV.png\"/>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/deimos-fabric-forge-neoforge\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/83sD0W8.png\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/deimos\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j2GIPnt.png\"/></a>\n</p></center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/marstheplanet\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rJIRiP5.png\" /></a></p>",
